simple.io

Class DoubleParsePosition

  • java.lang.Object
    • simple.io.DoubleParsePosition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public final class DoubleParsePosition
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Object to hold start and end positions.
    Start and end positions can be marked and restored.
    Has several convenience methods.
    Created: Sep 12, 2010
    Author:
    Kenneth Pierce
